		<h6>Third-party links on our websites</h6>
		<p>Our SERVICE may contain links to third-party websites. Please be aware that ASROCK is not responsible for the security, the privacy practices and the materials of those third-party websites. We encourage you to be aware of when you leave our SERVICE, and to read the privacy statements of those third-party websites carefully. This Privacy Policy applies to ASROCK SERVICE only.</p>
		<h6>Security</h6>
		<p>We take precautions to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction. We conduct internal reviews of our information collection, storage and processing practices and security measures, as well as physical security measures to guard against unauthorized access to systems where we store your information. </p>
		<p>Transmission of information between different locations of ASROCK and its affiliated companies is performed through our secured wide area network. When you submit your information to us, your information is protected both online and offline.</p>
		<p>However, ASROCK cannot guarantee perfect security on the internet. To protect your data from unauthorized access, we recommend that you:</p>
		<ul class="Lists">
			<li>To use alphanumerical passwords when signing up ASROCK Member account.</li>
			<li>To change your passwords on a regular basis.</li>
			<li>To keep your devices up to date by applying the latest available security updates for your software and use such tools as virus/spyware scanners.</li>
		</ul>
		<p>If you become aware of a technical vulnerability affecting ASROCK SERVICE, please do not hesitate to contact us through <a href="mailto:privacy@asrock.com.tw">privacy@asrock.com.tw</a></p>
		<h5>Manage Your Information</h5>
		<p>We want to help you keep your information accurate. You may view and change your information by logging in your ASROCK Member account and editing your account information. </p>
		<p>For further inquiries about information ASROCK collect about you, kindly contact us through <a href="mailto:privacy@asrock.com.tw">privacy@asrock.com.tw</a></p>
		<p>Whenever you use our SERVICE, we strive to maintain the accuracy of your data and protect your information against any accidental or malicious destruction. We will accommodate your requests regarding your data; however, we may not be able to fulfill all your requests in the following circumstances:</p>
